
PerfFX gathers basic JavaFX application to perform performance tests (Marlin renderer + prism):

* Requirements:
    * OpenJDK 11+
    * GraalVM Community Edition (CE) 19.3.1+
    * Maven (gluon) plugin

* Run JavaFX (jvm):
    mvn javafx:run

* Build native image:
    mvn client:build

* Run native image:
    ./target/client/x86_64-linux/PerfFX

Enjoy FOSS !

